welcome_description:
Gqibezela esi sifundo sifutshane ukuze ufumane ibhonasi yokufundisa ekhethekileyo.

Kuya kuthatha umzuzu nje!
free_spins_description:
Yonke imihla okanye iveki xa ungena, iakhawunti yakho iya kunikwa yonke imihla 'i-Spins yasimahla' kunye 'neeBhokisi zeMfihlakalo' ngeveki.

Inombolo oyifumanayo ixhomekeke kwinqanaba le-akhawunti yakho.
daily_streak_description:
Yonke imihla ungena kwaye uzuze inani elincinci leeNkozo zemali, ungabanga umkhondo wakho wemihla ngemihla.

Okukhona usiba neentsuku ezilandelelanayo, kokukhona uya kuba mkhulu umvuzo!

Amanqanaba aphezulu eakhawunti nawo afumana umvuzo omkhulu.
ptc_ads_description:
Jonga iintengiso zePTC ngokukhawuleza, iintengiso ezimfutshane ukonyusa inani lemali yakho yemihla ngemihla.

Intengiso iya kuvula kwithebhu entsha, ke qiniseka ukuba ihlala ivuliwe de isibali-xesha senziwe!
missions_description:
Uya kufumana amakhulu eemishini kunye nezicelo ekufuneka uzigqibe kwicandelo 'leMishini' lewebhusayithi.

Ukugqibezela imisebenzi kunye nezicelo yindlela entle yokufumana iiNkozo zemali zebhonasi.

Jonga i-Fuza → 'iMishini yeBhonasi' iphepha ngeenkcukacha.
offers_description:
Ukugqiba izibonelelo yenye yeendlela ezilungileyo zokufumana iiNkozo kwiGigaFaucet.

Unikezelo lunokufumaneka kwicandelo elithi 'Zuza' lewebhusayithi.

Kukho iintlobo ezininzi ezahlukeneyo zonikezelo ezikhoyo. Qiniseka ukuba uzijongele ezo zikusebenzela ngcono.
xp_description:
Ngalo lonke ixesha ugqiba isibonelelo, udlala i-multiplier, okanye ubukele ividiyo, njl.njl., uya kufumana i-XP (Amanqaku amava).

Ukufumana i-XP kuya kuphucula iakhawunti yakho, kuvuleke iimpawu ezininzi kunye nemivuzo emikhulu.

Ungafumana inqanaba leakhawunti yakho kwiphepha lakho leProfayili okanye leeBhonasi.
withdraw_description:
Ungazirhoxisa iiNkozo zakho xa sele ubethe ubuncinci beziinkozo ezingama-30,000.

Ukurhoxisa, yiya kwi-Akhawunti → 'Imali ephumayo' kwaye ukhethe indlela yokurhola oyikhethayo.

Landela imiyalelo ukugqiba ukurhoxa kwakho.
all_set_description:
Ngoku ukulungele ukuqala ukufumana iiNkozo kwiGigaFaucet!

Khumbula ukujonga umva imihla ngemihla ukuze ufumane i-spins yakho yebhonasi kunye neebhokisi ezifihlakeleyo, kunye nezibonelelo ezipheleleyo kunye nemishini yokwandisa umvuzo wakho.

Ithamsanqa kwaye wonwabe!
